                        <interp inst="t18430508-name-766" type="given" value="WILLIAM HENRY"></interp>WILLIAM HENRY WOOD</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in John-street—I saw the prisoner go up the steps of Mr. Bygrove's shop, and take a pair of boots out of the window—he came out, and ran down Martha-street, and two more boys after him—Mrs. Bygrove came out, and I told her which way he had gone.</p>
